            "title": "遠東宏信半年純利按年升3.8% 維持中期息每股0.25元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">遠東宏信(03360)公布，上半年純利21.64億元人民幣，按年升3.8%；維持派中期息每股0.25港元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15139718-%e9%81%a0%e6%9d%b1%e5%ae%8f%e4%bf%a1%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%873-8-%e7%b6%ad%e6%8c%81%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a10-25%e5%85%83",
