            "title": "內地A股早市窄幅爭持 油股回吐 中石化盈警後捱沽",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深股市今早陷入窄幅爭持局面，兩市股指半日反覆微跌；油價回落，油股隨之回吐，中國石化(00386)發盈警後沽壓較明顯。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國石化微博\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石化2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國石化微博\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240411_FI_source-web_中國石化2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國石化微博</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開4點後呈好淡爭持局面，半日高位3581點時僅升8點，低位3563點時亦只跌9點，高低位相差只得17點；滬指中午收報3566點，跌6點或0.19%，半日成交4252.56億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指早市大部份時間報升，最高曾見11068點，回升58點，後段卻轉跌，最低見10984點，跌24點；深指中午收報10992點，跌16點或0.15%，成交5696億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌10點或0.25%，收報4065點；創業板指數則倒跌3點或0.16%，報2324點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中石化昨收市後發盈警，今早A、H齊跌，H股最多跌逾5%，中石化A股(600028.SH)也跌4.83%，報5.72元，成交13.53億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">石油行業板塊內股份亦普遍跟隨油價回吐，細價股山東墨龍(00568)A股(002490.SZ)跌2.67%，報6.19元。中國石油(00857)A股(601857.SH)也跌2.93%，報8.61元；中海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)跌0.5%，報26.03元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15139525-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e6%b2%b9%e8%82%a1%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e4%b8%ad%e7%9f%b3%e5%8c%96%e7%9b%88%e8%ad%a6%e5%be%8c%e6%8d%b1%e6%b2%bd",
